What you need to know:

Saturday’s event which also comes after Friday’s curtain-raiser club-night at the giant Thika Greens Golf Resort, has like last year’s tournament, attracted a huge field of 252 playersLike last year, the Ruiru leg of the series has received great support from more than 40 golfers from Machakos and of course staff and guests of the sponsors ICEA Lion GroupDue to the big field drawn, Saturday’s event at Ruiru is set for 6.50am with an early afternoon tee-off of 11am